g/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLoOsXdt.jpg&h=b1104862&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">每晚10點</span></strong></span>大家開大嗰窗嗌口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當係抒發下或者互相鼓勵都好<br />\n<br />\n真係有人嗌㗎 唔洗怕醜<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fit.tsoi/videos/189596038709864/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffit.tsoi%2Fvideos%2F189596038709864%2F&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTLe6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=528ca6eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/fit.tsoi/videos/189596038709864/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1170684516349159/posts/2398098013607797?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1170684516349159%2Fposts%2F2398098013607797%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTLe6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=968b197c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1170684516349159/posts/2398098013607797?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/102458676557543/posts/1582783125191750?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F102458676557543%2Fposts%2F1582783125191750%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTLe6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=b62b7cc9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/102458676557543/posts/1582783125191750?sfns=mo</a><br />\n將窗嗌口號變成一種普及的生活方式，會好大感染力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cyn9vh9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcyn9vh9.png&h=f1d434e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"223cd93c6d465aaa10d504bfad5d1bf4480af61b","tid":1514962,"uid":2507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:08:40.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母 死黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc03970c696cfb6bbf4a902bdd3ec0c6dfb29350","tid":1514962,"uid":35842,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:09:58.000Z","msg":"[一齊拎no no]<br />\n利申有三幾次拎不反對通知書嘅經驗<br />\n<br />\n2017年7月1號香港民族黨舉行淪陷20年悼念晚會，唔單止拎唔到不反對，而且收到禁止集會通知書(唔係反對)，再宣傳該集會，已經可以被拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n當你拎唔到不反對，你係可以上訴，咁佢要揾幾個社會賢達，例如退休法官，組個panel處理。果次上訴 #香港警察 請哂律師，然後整理哂香港民族黨或我個人嘅街站、集會紀錄，cap網上啲留言呀(you no gun you yes gun果類無聊野)，呢樣果樣整個powerpoint。當然你都要申述啦，我冇野講都得嘅。搞左個上晝，否決左我嘅上訴。<br />\n<br />\n香港作為一個發達嘅公民社會，人人都可以去申請不反對搞遊行集會。例如我號召全球華人，參加撐港獨遊行，山東街頭行到尾，預計1000萬人參與，我行入任何一間警署就可以申請，唔批可以上訴。<br />\n<br />\n你知啦，香港而家個個禮拜示威，又冇大台，同一時間有一千幾百人申請不反對有幾閒，50人廣東道遊行街頭至街尾，50萬人中聯辦門口集會，299人中國外交部特派專員公署前集會，400萬人遊行過紅隧。唔批嘅話，我咪上訴囉，你又要揾幾個社會賢達嚟處理。<br />\n<br />\n#公安條例 #惡法 #不反對通知書 #nono<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/690555129/posts/10158599279295130?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F690555129%2Fposts%2F10158599279295130%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTLe6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=0a1040d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/690555129/posts/10158599279295130?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"0994c8c28a4b7f79961a4bd0f0fb9feac033a17f","tid":1514962,"uid":165610,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:10:43.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"855362146c4bc9a692ecfc020c17b96dd51b5719","tid":1514962,"uid":251775,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:10:50.000Z","msg":"你慌佢唔係做俾支聯辦睇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又多樣證據支共干預一國兩制 集會自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c7f3ce402a5f506065254e386a5acf3869ff789","tid":1514962,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite